entry.title: BeastlyGhost/FNF-Funkin-Feather
entry.summary:
a work in progress rewrite of NinjaMuffin99's Friday Night Funkin'

Funkin': Feather

A Work in Progress rewrite of Friday Night Funkin'.

Made for learning purposes and as a love letter for Friday Night Funkin's modding community. While still being very early in development, feedback and help with this project is appreciated.

The base game won't be included with Funkin': Feather, as it's made specifically for mods and mods only. However, it will be distributed separately, like a mod in it of itself.

Want to contact me?

You can do so on either Twitter or Discord.
